    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款FPS刷宝生存射击游戏。</h2>玩家在后世界末日的环境中扮演幸存者。<br><br><strong>核心玩法：</strong>搜刮、战斗、撤离、制造、改装。<br><br><strong>玩法循环：</strong>进入冒险区搜刮资源；消灭或躲避敌人；与其他幸存者互动；携带战利品在冒险中撤离回安全屋；在安全屋制造装备、改装武器、构筑能力；进入更危险的地区，获取更优越的战利品。<br><br>因此，这也是一款包含了捡垃圾、打僵尸、物品制造、武器改装、角色能力构筑、永久死亡和营地经营等玩法元素的末日生存游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>枪匠系统，打造富有想象力的武器<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/542b0ac268ebeb83cac8969c78aa1411.poster.avif?t=1725854920\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/542b0ac268ebeb83cac8969c78aa1411.webm?t=1725854920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/542b0ac268ebeb83cac8969c78aa1411.mp4?t=1725854920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>地图探索和地图随机特征<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/990716e491f22078d8744cf29893c0a6.poster.avif?t=1725854920\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/990716e491f22078d8744cf29893c0a6.webm?t=1725854920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/990716e491f22078d8744cf29893c0a6.mp4?t=1725854920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/68a1ac8640274b57482ab08f95ef1e34.poster.avif?t=1725854920\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/68a